  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">This letter was presumably addressed to Mrs. Maria Weston Chapman. Hannah M. Bevan thanks Maria W. Chapman for her kind note, which she values enough to keep in her &quot;work box and often look at with feelings of lively emotion.&quot; She refers to the &quot;self-sacrificing exertions&quot; of Maria W. Chapman. Bevan also thanks Maria W. Chapman for sending her a copy of the Liberty Bell.</subfield>
